{"exportVersion":"training-knowledge-export-v1","exportedAt":"2026-03-24T23:57:41.374Z","latestAudit":{"source":"scheduler","summary":"整体判断略偏乐观而且表述失真明显：真正的系统性问题不是单纯 GOOD 太多或 CLONE 太多，而是本地模型仍会把 capability / model / infra 包装成可创业产品，同时 one-liner 持续泛化；但在少数有明确团队工作流边界的 developer tool 上又会压成 CLONE。","severity":"HIGH","auditedAt":"2026-03-24T14:03:49.910Z","overallBias":{"reason":"Claude 复核里存在 8 个 local GOOD -> Claude OK，且 training hints 多次指出 false_positive_good、capability_as_product、model_or_infra_leakage、inconsistent GOOD flags。说明当前更大的系统性偏差仍是把能力层、模型层、基础设施层过早拔高为 GOOD；虽然也存在少量 developer workflow 工具被压成 CLONE，但数量和危险性都次于前者。","direction":"too_optimistic"},"suggestions":["把 rule family 的第一优先级放在 product reality：先判仓库本体是 product/tool 还是 model/infra/demo/template，再讨论创业性。","强制 GOOD 前做四字段一致性校验：hasRealUser、hasClearUseCase、hasProductizationPath、isDirectlyMonetizable 任意关键项为 false 时默认不得给 GOOD，除非明确解释例外。","重写 one-liner 提示词：必须包含具体用户、具体动作、具体工作流对象，禁止“帮团队提效”“自动跑流程”“更容易部署上线”这类占位语。","补 capability-as-product 的 CLONE anchors：LLM router/proxy、fallback daemon、本地 agent memory service、MCP server framework、模型推理仓库。","补 developer workflow GOOD anchors：人工审批/审计控制台、预算治理、团队级安全审批、清晰 devops/release 控制面。","给 infra/security 增加负向启发式：eBPF、iptables、packet capture、kernel visibility、低层拦截能力默认先审为 infra，不因技术亮点升 GOOD。","给 template/demo 增加更早的识别规则，尤其对 framework、starter repo、reference implementation、single-file demo 和 portfolio/project scaffold。","不要把“同类很多”当作唯一降级理由，但也不要把“可包装成 SaaS”当作升 GOOD 的理由，必须给出明确 buyer 和采购切口。"],"problemTypes":[{"type":"one_liner_drift","count":30,"examples":[]},{"type":"capability_or_infra_as_product","count":9,"examples":[{"reason":"本地曾将其拔到 GOOD，但它更像本地 LLM proxy/router 能力层，不是可直接售卖的完整产品。","fullName":"kianwoon/modelweaver","repositoryId":"cmn2znmhj0dgxl57aurc3ruus","currentAction":"CLONE","currentVerdict":"OK","suggestedAction":"CLONE","suggestedVerdict":"OK"}]},{"type":"false_positive_good","count":8,"examples":[{"reason":"本地把拥挤且泛化的 AI 求职应用高估为 GOOD，Claude 纠正为 OK。","fullName":"shilpasathyanarayana/resume-opt